      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Candidate A demonstrates a highly professional communication style, using precise language and a structured approach that instills confidence in a client-facing role. In contrast, Candidate B relies on informal contractions, slang, and casual phrasing that may undermine their credibility with serious business stakeholders. For a customer success position, Candidate A is the clear choice as their demeanor and vocabulary align perfectly with maintaining trust and professionalism.",
